    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "所以是ENTITY-DATA、LOCATION-DATA、PRODUCT-DATA、ITEM-DATA四个表，每个都有value字段，并关联对应的实体和DATA-TYPE？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ENTITY-DATA",
