    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，value用text类型，DATA-TYPE有name和note。所有扩展数据都必须有类型和所属实体，是多对一关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
